0team%20from%20carmaker%20Porsche%20submitted%20a%20report%20today%20stating%20there%20were%20no%20issues%20with%20the%20car.%20The%20inspection%20by%20the%20Porsche%20team%20is%20part%20of%20the%20criminal%20investigation%20carried%20out%20against%20the%20teenager%2C%20who%20is%20in%20the%20remand%20home%20till%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accident%2C%20which%20left%20software%20engineers%20Ashwini%20Kostha%20and%20Aneesh%20Awadhiya%20dead%2C%20sparked%20nationwide%20outrage%20after%20the%20teen%20was%20granted%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20of%20the%20accident%20on%20conditions%20widely%20seen%20as%20flimsy%20--%20a%20300-word%20essay%2C%2015%20days%20of%20work%20with%20traffic%20police%20and%20psychiatric%20treatment%20and%20counselling%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20modified%20its%20order%20and%20sent%20him%20to%20an%20observation%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minor's%20father%2C%20mother%20and%20grandfather%20were%20arrested%20over%20their%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20crime.%20The%20teenager's%20mother%2C%20Shivani%20Agrawal%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20June%201%2C%20after%20a%20probe%20revealed%20she%20allegedly%20swapped%20her%20blood%20sample%20with%20the%20boy's%20during%20a%20medical%20test%20to%20determine%20whether%20the%20teenager%20was%20drunk%20or%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20also%20trying%20to%20recover%20the%20original%20blood%20sample%20of%20the%20minor%2C%20which%20was%20allegedly%20replaced%20to%20get%20him%20off%20the%20hook.%20Two%20doctors%20of%20the%20state-run%20Sassoon%20Hospital%2C%20including%20the%20head%20of%20the%20forensic%20department%2C%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20switching%20blood%20samples%20to%20manipulate%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20taken%20custody%20of%20his%20father%2C%20realtor%20Vishal%20Agrawal%2C%20arrested%20earlier%20in%20a%20related%20case%2C%20for%20allegedly%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20destruction%20of%20evidence.%20The%20accused's%20grandfather%20has%20been%20sent%20to%2014-day%20judicial%20custody%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20accident%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20alleged%20that%20the%20grandfather%20and%20the%20father%20threatened%20their%20driver%2C%20snatched%20his%20phone%20and%20forcible%20kept%20him%20confined%20in%20their%20bungalow%20to%20force%20him%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20crime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20an%20observation%20home%20as%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20takes%20a%20call%20on%20the%20police%20request%20to%20try%20him%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20was%20caught%20on%20camera%20drinking%20shortly%20before%20the%20accident%20occurred%20and%20had%20allegedly%20spent%20Rs%2048%2C000%20at%20a%20pub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20interrogation%2C%20the%20teen%20has%20claimed%20an%20inability%20to%20recollect%20what%20happened%20that%20night%2C%20the%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20accident%20after%20the%20crime%20branch's%20investigation%20revealed%20an%20elaborate%20plot%20to%20shield%20the%20teen%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717413120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Feoj00p2o_pune-porsche-_625x300_22_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-issues-with-vehicle-porsche-inspects-car-that-killed-2-in-pune-5806803%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20team%20from%20Porsche%20inspected%20the%20car%20that%20killed%20two%20engineers%20in%20Pune%20on%20May%2019.%20The%20car%2C%20allegedly%20driven%20by%20a%2017-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20Pune%20realtor%2C%20rammed%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20on%20a%20bike.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-issues-with-vehicle-porsche-i