polling%20station%20in%20Palnadu%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20videos%20widely%20circulated%20online%2C%20the%20ruling%20YSR%20Congress'%20P%20Ramakrishna%20Reddy%20-%20backed%20by%20a%20few%20equally%20unruly%20supporters%20-%20was%20shown%20barging%20into%20a%20voting%20booth%2C%20grabbing%20the%20EVM%20(electronic%20voting%20machine)%20and%20VVPAT%20(voter%20verified%20paper%20trail)%20off%20the%20table%2C%20and%20throwing%20it%20to%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20on%20May%2013.%20Within%20days%2C%20however%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20had%20received%20protection%20in%20that%20and%20associated%20cases%2C%20with%20High%20Court%20Justice%20Venkata%20Jyothirmayi's%20interim%20orders%20directing%20police%20not%20to%20act%20against%20the%20lawmaker%20till%2010%20am%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20are%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20though%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Justices%20Arvind%20Kumar%20and%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20asked%20serious%20questions%20of%20the%20High%20Court's%20decision%2C%20which%20they%20called%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20mockery%20of%20the%20system%26quot%3B.%20The%20top%20court%20also%20said%20it%20was%20minded%20to%20cancel%20the%20interim%20protection%2C%20which%20would%20have%20left%20Mr%20Reddy%20open%20to%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(How%20can%20the%20court%20give)%20interim%20protection%20in%20such%20cases...%20if%20we%20do%20not%20stay%20this%20order%2C%20it%20will%20amount%20to%20mockery%20of%20the%20system...%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kumar%20said%20after%20a%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20was%20played.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20we%20being%20made%20fun%20of%3F%20This%20is%20a%20sheer%20joke.%20How%20can%20so%20many%20enter%20a%20polling%20booth%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20live%20web%20telecast...%20the%20complainant%20said%20both%20EVM%20and%20VVPAT%20were%20snatched%20and%20destroyed...%20eight%20people%20(were)%20inside%20the%20polling%20booth.%20Where%20is%20the%20question%20of%20bail%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20raged%2C%20adding%20it%20was%20inclined%2C%20prima%20facie%2C%20to%20accept%20allegations%20made%20against%20the%20YSRCP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-camera-andhra-mla-flings-vvpat-to-ground-in-polling-booth-5715873%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOn%20Camera%2C%20Andhra%20MLA%20Flings%20VVPAT%20To%20Ground%20In%20Polling%20Booth%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20doctored%20video...%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it...%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Mehta%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20criticised%20the%20MLA%20for%20remaining%20hidden%20till%20the%20interim%20protection%20order%2C%20and%20also%20the%20cops%20for%20their%20response%20to%20the%20shocking%20incident.%20%26quot%3B...he%20is%20belittling%20the%20system.%20Sitting%20MLA%20goes%20to%20the%20polling%20station%2C%20destroys%20EVM%20and%20VVPAT%2C%20and%20complaint%20is%20filed%20about%20'unknown%20person'%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%2Fsupreme-court-bars-andhra-mla-who-smashed-evm-from-entering-counting-station-on-june-4-5805360%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndhra%20MLA%20Who%20Smashed%20EVM%20Barred%20From%20Counting%20Station%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irate%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20however%2C%20settled%20for%20barring%20Mr%20Reddy%20from%20entering%20the%20vote%20counting%20booth%20in%20his%20constituency%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20YSRCP%20leader%20was%20told%20he%20was%20not%20allowed%20in%20the%20vicinity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20technicality%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20the%20High%20Court%20to%20hear%20cases%20registered%20against%20Mr%20Reddy%20-%20listed%20for%20Thursday%20-%20'without%20being%20influe