sraeli%20passports%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresidency.gov.mv%2FPress%2FArticle%2F30948%5C%22%3Estatement%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20his%20office.%20However%2C%20no%20official%20details%20were%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%20president's%20office%20further%20said%20that%20the%20Cabinet%20decided%20to%20amend%20necessary%20laws%C2%A0to%20prevent%20Israeli%20passport%20holders%20from%20entering%20the%20country%20and%20further%20establish%20a%20subcommittee%20to%20oversee%20these%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20has%20also%20announced%20a%20national%20fundraising%20campaign%20in%20support%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20to%20conduct%20a%20nationwide%20rally%20--%20%E2%80%9CMaldivians%20in%20Solidarity%20with%20Palestine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20the%20Maldives%20banned%20Israeli%20citizens%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20--%20a%20sign%20of%20protest%20against%20Israel's%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Gaza%20--%20to%20ban%20Israeli%20passport%20holders%20comes%20amid%20growing%20pressure%20on%20President%20Muizzu%20from%20Opposition%20parties%20as%20well%20as%20his%20allies%20in%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20came%20days%20after%20Mr%20Muizzu%20condemned%20the%20Israeli%20airstrike%20that%20triggered%20a%20fire%20that%20killed%2045%20people%20in%20a%20tent%20camp%20in%20Rafah%20over%20a%20week%20ago.%20This%20region%20was%20earlier%20deemed%20a%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20zone%26quot%3B%20for%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStrongly%20condemn%20the%20deadly%20attack%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20on%20the%20tent%20camp%20in%20Rafah%2C%20where%20displaced%20Palestinians%20were%20taking%20shelter.%20Israel%20must%20abide%20by%20the%20ICJ%20rulings.%20No%20country%20is%20exempt%20from%20international%20law.%20Together%20with%20the%20Government%20and%20people%20of%20Maldives%2C%20I%20call%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%2C%20an%20end%20to%20violence%20and%20unhindered%20humanitarian%20access%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20social%20media%20site%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EStrongly%20condemn%20the%20deadly%20attack%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20on%20the%20tent%20camp%20in%20Rafah%2C%20where%20displaced%20Palestinians%20were%20taking%20shelter.%20Israel%20must%20abide%20by%20the%20ICJ%20rulings.%20No%20country%20is%20exempt%20from%20international%20law.%20Together%20with%20the%20Government%20and%20people%20of%20Maldives%2C%20I%20call%20for%20an%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20(%40MMuizzu)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMMuizzu%2Fstatus%2F1795251055678177409%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIsrael's%20advisory%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20ban%2C%20the%20Israeli%20foreign%20ministry%20recommended%20its%20citizens%20avoid%20travelling%20to%20Maldives.%20The%20recommendation%20also%20included%20Israelis%20holding%20dual%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Israeli%20citizens%20already%20in%20the%20country%2C%20it%20is%20recommended%20to%20consider%20leaving%2C%20because%20if%20they%20find%20themselves%20in%20distress%20for%20any%20reason%2C%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20assist%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fisrael-recommends-that-its-citizens-avoid-maldives-2024-06-03%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520recommendation%252C%2520the%2520Israeli%2520ministry%2Cministry%2520said%2520in%2520a%2520statement.%5C%22%3Estatement%20from%20the%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20earlier%20lifted%20a%20previous%20ban%20on%20tourists%20from%20Israel%20during%20the%20early%201990s%20and%20further%20moved%20towards%20restoring%20relations%20in%202010.%20The%20normalisation%20attempts%2C%20however%2C%20saw%20r