E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Single-Agenda%20Election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20general%20election%20will%20go%20down%20in%20India's%20political%20history%20as%20a%20single-agenda%20election.%20Do%20you%20want%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-pens-his-thoughts-on-indias-future-after-45-hour-meditation-full-text-5804299%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20continue%20being%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%3F%20The%20voter%20responded%20to%20this%20simple%20question.%20Nothing%20more%2C%20nothing%20less.%20If%20the%20exit%20poll%20numbers%20are%20correct%2C%20the%20nation%20has%20responded%20with%20a%20resounding%20yes.%20Not%20just%20the%20number%20of%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20also%20projected%20to%20claim%20a%20historic%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnda-to-get-over-350-seats-pm-modi-will-return-for-third-term-poll-of-exit-polls-5794694%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0PM%20Modi%20Hat-Trick%2C%20Powered%20By%20South%2C%20Bengal%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Predict%20Exit%20Polls%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20it%20mean%20for%20the%20future%20of%20Indian%20politics%3F%20Simply%20put%2C%20the%20voter%20is%20likely%20to%20put%20more%20trust%20in%20the%20known%20devil%20than%20the%20unchartered%20waters%20of%20the%20deep%20sea.%20People%20have%20either%20given%20the%20incumbent%20government%20their%20approval%20or%20have%20made%20peace%20with%20them.%20A%20curious%20mix%20of%20optimism%20and%20fatalism.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20we%20must%20remember%20that%20electoral%20contestation%2C%20however%20vigorous%20and%20vibrant%2C%20is%20not%20an%20antidote%20to%20authoritarianism.%20Elections%20are%20not%20a%20panacea%20for%20all%20socio-political%20ills%20in%20any%20society.%20They%20are%2C%20most%20certainly%2C%20a%20managing%20mechanism%20for%20the%20malaise%20of%20authoritarianism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20rigging%20to%20religious%20fundamentalism%20to%20reconfirmed%20faith%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20%C2%A0theories%20abound.%20Only%20the%20perfect%20hindsight%20of%20history%20will%20tell%20us%20the%20truth%20behind%20the%202024%20verdict.%20The%20only%20thing%20left%20to%20be%20done%20immediately%20by%20everyone%20involved%20is%20the%20commitment%20to%20accountability.%20A%20lot%20has%20been%20talked%20about%20the%20accountability%20of%20institutions%20and%20systems.%20Let's%20shift%20the%20focus%20to%20the%20citizenry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemocracy%20Is%20A%20Love%20Affair%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20scientists%20Juan%20Linz%20and%20Alfred%20Stepan%20see%20democracy%20as%20a%20vulnerable%20system%20unless%20both%20masses%20and%20elites%20develop%20favourable%20attitudes%20towards%20it.%20Robert%20Putnam%20takes%20it%20a%20bit%20further%20to%20insist%20that%20it's%20the%20actions%20and%20not%20the%20beliefs%20of%20citizens%20that%20strengthen%20democracy.%20So%2C%20do%20we%20the%20people%20really%20want%20democracy%3F%20If%20yes%2C%20do%20we%20act%20like%20we%20do%3F%20Democratic%20processes%20are%20just%20like%20love%20affairs.%20Words%20and%20beliefs%2C%20though%20important%2C%20mean%20nothing%20if%20not%20followed%20by%20congruent%20actions%20in%20both%20cases.%20Thus%2C%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20people%20claim%20to%20espouse%20the%20cause%20of%20democracy%20in%20letter%2C%20spirit%2C%20and%20action%2C%20the%20question%20remains%20-%20do%20they%20champion%20universal%20democracy%20or%20a%20restricted%20one%3F%20There%20is%20a%20tendency%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20elite%2C%20to%20deny%20agency%20and%20even%20intelligence%20to%20anyone%20except%20'people%20like%20us'.%20Thus%20qualified%20democracy%20is%20a%20Trojan%20horse.%20This%20is%20how%20authoritarianism%20creeps%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople's%20Achievement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20India's%20unstable%20socio-politi