n%20175%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fruja-ignatova-fbis-most-wanted-scammer-behind-4-billion-fraud-3716181%5C%22%3EWho%20Is%20Ruja%20Ignatova%20And%20How%20She%20Disappeared%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20carried%20out%20an%20investigation%20that%20seeks%20to%20answer%20the%20question%20-%20what%20happened%20to%20Dr%20Ignatova%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20lasted%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20said%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20revealed%20her%20close%20ties%20to%20a%20suspected%20Bulgarian%20organised%20crime%20boss%20-%20Hristoforos%20Nikos%20Amanatidis%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20Taki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20told%2C%20allegedly%20a%20big-time%20drug%20guy%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20her%20physical%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Richard%20Reinhardt%2C%20who%20began%20the%20investigation%20into%20OneCoin%20for%20the%20US%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service%20alongside%20the%20FBI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc2llvlx2ez9o%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaki%20came%20up%20more%20than%20once%2C%20it%20wasn't%20like%20it%20was%20a%20one-off.%20That%20was%20a%20recurring%20theme%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20now-retired%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20boarded%20a%20plane%20in%20Bulgaria%20with%20Taki%2C%20her%20bodyguard%2C%20and%20flew%20to%20Athens.%20The%20bodyguard%20returned%20and%20she%20did%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20have%20evidence%20that%20a%20very%20significant%2C%20if%20not%20the%20most%20prolific%2C%20drug%20trafficker%20of%20all%20time%20in%20Bulgaria%2C%20was%20closely%20linked%20to%20OneCoin%20-%20served%20as%20Ruja%20Ignatova's%20personal%20security%20guard%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20assistant%20attorney%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaki%20is%20a%20big%20name%20in%20Bulgaria%2C%20like%20El%20Chapo%20or%20Pablo%20Escobar.%20He%20is%20widely%20suspected%20of%20being%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Bulgarian%20organised%20crime%20network%20and%20a%20prolific%20drug%20smuggler.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20documents%20accessed%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20police%20suspect%20Taki%20of%20using%20OneCoin's%20financial%20network%20to%20launder%20the%20proceeds%20of%20drug%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaki%20is%20the%20ghost.%20You'll%20never%20see%20him.%20You%20only%20hear%20about%20him.%20He's%20talking%20to%20you%20through%20other%20people.%20If%20you%20don't%20listen%2C%20you%20just%20disappear%20from%20earth.%20The%20only%20person%20who%20can%20protect%20Ignatova%20from%20all%20those%20investigations%2C%20including%20from%20foreign%20agencies%20-%20it%20was%20Taki%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20former%20Bulgarian%20deputy%20minister%2C%20Ivan%20Hristanov.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaki%20now%20reportedly%20lives%20in%20Dubai.%20Bulgarian%20insiders%20said%20Ms%20Ignatova%20paid%20100%2C000%20euros%20(Rs%2090.2%20lakh)%20a%20month%20to%20him%20for%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20end%2C%20Ms%20Ignatova's%20protector%20may%20have%20turned%20aggressor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20a%202022%20report%20by%20Bulgarian%20investigative%20journalist%20Dimitar%20Stoyanov%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20that%20Ms%20Ignatova%20was%20killed%20a%20year%20after%20her%20disappearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journalist%20presented%20a%20police%20report%20that%20details%20overhearing%20Taki's%20brother-in-law%20drunkenly%20saying%20Ms%20Ignatova%20had%20been%20murdered%20on%20Taki's%20orders%20in%20late%202018%2C%20and%20her%20body%20dismembered%20and%20dumped%20off%20a%20yacht%20in%20the%20Ionian%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20criminal%20associates%20of%20Taki%20claimed%20Ms%20Ignatova%20had%20become%20a%20liability%20for%20him.%20Property%20records%20show%20that%20since%20Ms%20Ignatova's%20disappearance%2C%20a%20number%20of%20her%20properties%20are%20now%20being%20used%20by%20people%20connected%20to%20Taki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaki%20has%20never%20been%20arrested%20over%20the%20claims%20of%20Ms%20Ignatova's%20murder.%20Her%20body%20has%20never%20been%20found%20and%20investigators%20say%20they%20don't%20have%20enough%20evidence%20to%20prosecute%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20rumours%20still%20circulate%20that%20the%20news%20of%20her%20death%20is%20another%20brilliant%20manoeuvre%20to%20throw%20everyone%20off%20the%20scent.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717400880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fdlmlijb8_ruja-ignatova_625x300_03_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fruja-ignatova-fbis-most-wanted-scammer-disappeared-with-4-billion-now-shes-been-linked-to-bulgarian-underworld-5805725%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Quoting%20a%202022%20report%20by%20Bulgarian%20investigative%20journalist%20Dimitar%20Stoyanov%2C%20the%20BBC%20said%20that%20Ruja%20Ignatova%20was%20killed%20a%20year%20after%20her%20disappearance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fruja-ignatova-fbis-most-wanted-scammer-disappeared-with-4-billion-now-shes-been-linked-to-bulgarian-underworld-5805725%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fruja-ignatova-fbis-most-wanted-scammer-disappeared-with-4-billion-now-shes-been-linked-to-bulgarian-underworld-5805725%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fruja-ignatova-fbis-most-wanted-scammer-disappeared-with-4-billion-now-shes-been-linked-to-bulgarian-underworld-5805725%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20you%20know%20Sridevi%20has%20a%20connection%20with%20Jr.%20NTR%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717400126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%