20must%20accept.%20One%20of%20those%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance's%20own%20295%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20while%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20largely%20managed%20a%20cohesive%20campaign%20on%20state-by-state%20local%20discontent%20and%20dodged%20a%20presidential-style%20personality%20clash%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20there%20was%20an%20inherent%20risk%20in%20that%20strategy.%20It%20articulated%20the%20economic%20and%20agrarian%20discontent%20in%20some%20key%20states%2C%20but%20was%20more%20dependent%20on%20local%20arithmetic%20and%20not%20building%20a%20national%20chemistry.%20It%20did%20not%20have%20a%20concrete%20face%20as%20the%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%20it%20states%20of%20a%20categorical%20strong%20face%20in%20power.%20The%20Congress's%20manifesto%20offered%20promise%2C%20but%20who%20was%20the%20face%20who%20would%20deliver%20that%20promise%3F%20It%20was%20damned%20if%20it%20did%20have%20a%20PM%20candidate%20and%20damned%20if%20didn't%2C%20before%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20states%20like%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20swept%20assembly%20polls%2C%20its%20campaign%20revolved%20around%20categorical%20chief%20ministerial%20faces.%20It's%20an%20indication%20that%20an%20anti-Modi%20political%20cohesion%20could%20not%20convince%20the%20electorate%20of%20a%20stable%20and%20strong%20offer%20of%20change%20and%20a%20personality%20to%20drive%20it.%20Even%20in%20the%20so-called%20opposition%20positive%20states%2C%20like%20a%20Karnataka%20or%20a%20Telangana%2C%20this%20was%20a%20weakness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%2C%20even%20in%20a%20state-by-state%20strategy%2C%20there%20was%20not%20a%20single%2C%20large%20or%20medium%2C%20direct%20Congress%20versus%20BJP%20state%20where%20the%20Congress%20could%20claim%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20on%20all%20or%20almost%20all%20seats.%20For%20instance%2C%20even%20in%20Karnataka%20-%20which%20is%20possibly%20the%20Congress's%20strongest%20state%20now%20-%20the%20most%20reasonably%20optimistic%20projection%20from%20analysts%2C%20and%20many%20within%20the%20party%2C%20was%2010-15%20seats.%20The%20party%20could%20not%20claim%20that%20it%20will%20entirely%20reverse%20the%20BJP's%202019%20performance%20of%2025%2F28.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20announces%20a%20sweep%2C%20it%20really%20is%20one.%20Even%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20while%20most%20observers%20and%20many%20exit%20polls%20indicate%20a%20revision%20from%20the%20BJP-Sena%20sweep%20of%202019%2C%20the%20opposition%20MVA%20could%20never%20claim%20a%20total%20sweep%20of%20even%2C%20say%2C%2040%20of%2048.%20This%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20is%20with%20the%20Congress%20now.%20A%20sweep%20of%20the%20kind%20a%20DMK%20alliance%20could%20claim%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20or%20the%20Congress%20could%20claim%20against%20the%20Left%20in%20Kerala%2C%20is%20absent%20anywhere%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguably%2C%20the%20above%20two%20failings%20are%20reflected%20in%20the%20295%20figure%20put%20out%20by%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20third%20factor.%20The%20opposition's%20number%20reflects%20a%20calculated%20aggregate%20of%20varying%20degrees%20of%20performance%20in%20individual%20states%2C%20both%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20be%20argued%20that%20the%20number%20does%20not%20reflect%20the%20confidence%20of%20a%20national%20sweep.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP's%20narrative%20was%20an%20overwhelming%20national%20sweep.%20While%20at%20the%20grassroots%20it%20worked%20on%20a%20state-by-state%20strategy%2C%20the%20overall%20narrative%20was%20a%20national%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20sweeping%26quot%3B%20script%20starring%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20Despite%20economic%20and%20social%20foundations%20for%20a%20strong%20narrative%2C%20the%20opposition%20could%20not%20convince%20itself%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20electorate%2C%20of%20a%20national%20reverse%20sweep%20of%20the%20scale%20the%20BJP%20projected.%20This%20may%20be%2C%20ultimately%2C%20the%20success%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B400-paar%26quot%3B%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20too%20much%20repetition%20of%20the%202004%20victory%20as%20an%20argument%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20win%20even%20without%20a%20PM%20face.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20realities%20have%20changed%20and%20after%20a%20decade%20of%20rule%20under%20one%20strong%20personality%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20coalition%20may%20not%20seem%20a%20dependable%20solution%2C%20not%20yet.%20The%20Congress%20needs%20to%20do%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20in%20the%20Hindi%20Heartland%20and%20in%20the%20direct%20BJP%20fight%20states%3B%20it%20needs%20to%20show%20it%20can%20sweep%20one%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf.%20And%20it's%20a%20big%20If%2C%20the%20exit%20polls%20numbers%20hold%20true%2C%20then%20it's%20a%20south%20eastern%20jolt%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20status%20quo%2C%20at%20best%20a%20continuum%2C%20in%20the%20north%20and%20west.%20A%20lesson%2C%20perhaps%2C%20that%20arithmetic%20is%20important%2C%20but%20national%20cohesive%20chemistry%20with%20a%20face%20to%20relate%20is%20essential.%20Especially%20with%20a%20Prime%20Minister%20who%20seems%20to%20have%20it%20in%20spades%20and%20a%20party%20that%20has%20mastered%20the%20art%20of%20converting%20it%20into%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(TM%20Veeraraghav%20is%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717399680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fhv3kbpq_rahul-gandhi-kharge_625x300_07_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-ndas-400-paar-vs-indias-at-least-295-lesson-for-congress-5805558%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20numbers%20flashing%20on%20TV%20screens%20from%20exit%20polls%20for%20Lok%20Sab