authorised%20to%20talk%20to%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20premier%20also%20plans%20to%20reduce%20import%20taxes%20on%20key%20inputs%20for%20locally-made%20goods%2C%20which%20have%20pushed%20up%20India's%20manufacturing%20costs%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20office%20and%20the%20labour%20and%20finance%20ministries%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Reuters'%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExit%20polls%20project%20that%20the%20right-wing%20coalition%20led%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20will%20win%20a%20big%20majority%20when%20election%20results%20are%20announced%20on%20June%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20reelection%20campaign%20was%20partly%20built%20on%20the%20promise%20of%20continued%20economic%20development.%20He's%20pitching%20India%20as%20an%20alternative%20for%20global%20firms%20diversifying%20their%20supply%20chains%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20world's%20fastest-growing%20major%20economy.%20But%20that%20includes%20both%20a%20booming%20tech%20sector%20and%20a%20struggling%20older%20economy%20that%20doesn't%20provide%20enough%20jobs%20for%20everyone%20else%2C%20said%20Josh%20Felman%2C%20the%20former%20head%20of%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund's%20office%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20can%20be%20done%20now%20to%20provide%20employment%20-%20good%20jobs%20for%20these%20people%20-%20is%20manufacturing%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Felman%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20successfully%20lured%20suppliers%20for%20major%20US%20corporations%20like%20Apple%20Inc%20and%20Alphabet%20Inc's%20Google.%20But%20less%20than%203%25%20of%20global%20manufacturing%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20country%2C%20compared%20to%2024%25%20for%20China%2C%20World%20Bank%20data%20shows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20plans%20to%20increase%20share%20of%20global%20manufacturing%20to%205%25%20by%202030%20and%2010%25%20by%202047%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20document%20seen%20by%20Reuters.%20It%20did%20not%20provide%20specifics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20spoke%20to%2015%20people%20-%20including%20bureaucrats%2C%20representatives%20of%20major%20investors%2C%20economists%20and%20trade%20unionists%20-%20who%20identified%20three%20significant%20obstacles%20holding%20back%20from%20manufacturing%20hub%20status%3A%20restrictive%20labour%20laws%2C%20challenges%20acquiring%20land%2C%20and%20a%20rigidly%20inefficient%20tariff%20regime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Pearl%20River%20Delta%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20PM%20Modi%20was%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%20between%202001%20and%202014%2C%20he%20dreamt%20up%20an%20investment%20zone%20in%20the%20Dholera%20region.%20Legislation%20creating%20the%20Dholera%20Special%20Investment%20Region%20(DSIR)%20was%20passed%20in%202009%20and%20local%20authorities%20began%20acquiring%20land%20for%20it%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20during%20a%202011%20visit%20to%20a%20Chinese%20port%2C%20was%20to%20develop%20DSIR%20along%20the%20%26quot%3BShanghai%20model%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20China%20set%20up%20special%20economic%20zones%20along%20its%20southeastern%20coast%20that%20are%20widely%20credited%20for%20it%20becoming%20the%20world's%20factory%20floor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELand%20reform%20was%20a%20precursor%20for%20China's%20manufacturing%20rise.%20Starting%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20Beijing%20separated%20ownership%20from%20usage%20rights%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20investors%20to%20acquire%20industrial%20land%2C%20said%20Henry%20Gao%2C%20a%20Chinese%20trade%20expert%20at%20Singapore%20Management%20University%20(SMU).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing's%20industrial%20zoning%20policies%20also%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20industries%20to%20set%20up%20in%20areas%20with%20ready%20access%20to%20materials%20and%20facilities%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20prime%20minister%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20continued%20to%20stress%20the%20importance%20of%20industrial%20zones%20for%20India.%20In%20March%2C%20he%20described%20facilities%20under%20construction%20in%20DSIR%20as%20central%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20semi-conductor%20manufacturing%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata%20Group%20announced%20plans%20in%20January%20to%20build%20India's%20first%20semi-conductor%20fabrication%20plant%20there.%20During%20a%20visit%20in%20March%2C%20Reuters%20also%20saw%20construction%20activity%20for%20an%20upcoming%20cargo%20airport%20and%20promotional%20billboards%20set%20up%20by%20real-estate%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20paved%20roads%20and%20a%20waterfront%20but%20little%20sign%20of%20bustling%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDSIR%20hopes%20to%20attract%20more%20manufacturing%20companies%20by%20providing%20leases%20of%20up%20to%2099%20years%20on%20government-owned%20land%2C%20said%20Rahul%20Gupta%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20Industrial%20Development%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20officials%20have%20said%20that%20it%20took%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20to%20acquire%20land%20and%20award%20infrastructure%20contracts%2C%20but%20Mr%20Gupta%20predicted%20there%20would%20be%20much%20more%20activity%20in%20about%20two%20to%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20such%20zones%2C%20industrial%20groups%20still%20have%20to%20undergo%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20difficult%20process%26quot%3B%20to%20acquire%20the%20large%20plots%20of%20land%20they%20need%20because%20title%20deeds%20are%20often%20unclear%20and%20holdings%20are%20fractured%2C%20said%20Richard%20Rossow%20of%20the%20Washington-based%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20think-tank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Foxconn%20-%20whose%20local%20investment%20was%20trumpeted%20as%20a%20major%20success%20by%20PM%20Modi%20-%20was%20met%20with%20protests%20by%20farmers%20in%20Karnataka%20unhappy%20with%20the%20compensation%20they%20received%20from%20local%20authorities%20for%20giving%20up%20their%20land%20to%20the%20manufacturer%2C%20Indian%20media%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Taiwanese%20company%20didn't%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3ELabour%20Struggles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20much%20of%20India%2C%20firms%20with%20more%20than%20100%20employees%20need%20authorisation%20from%20state%20governments%20to%20hire%20and%20fire.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prevents%20companies%20from%20adjusting%20their%20operations%20to%20meet%20demand%2C%20said%20Atul%20Gupta%2C%20partner%20at%20Bengalore%20law%20firm%20Trilegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-controlled%20parliament%20has%20passed%20legislation%20to%20raise%20the%20threshold%20before%20official%20approval%20to%20300%2C%20but%20state%20authorities%20that%20must%20consent%20to%20the%20changes%20have%20stalled%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20hopes%20that%20a%20strong%20win%20on%20June%204th%20will%20give%20him%20the%20momentum%20and%20political%20capital%20to%20push%20through%20their%20opposition%2C%20the%20two%20government%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20government%20wants%20to%20come%20across%20as%20giving%20permission%20to%20a%20company%20to%20let%20go%20of%20their%20employees%20(but)...this%20is%20just%20used%20to%20drag%20out%20the%20closure%20or%20the%20terminations%20endlessly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Gupta%2C%20who%20advocates%20labour%20reforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Motors%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20decided%20to%20shut%20plants%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Maharastra%20in%202017%2C%20citing%20low%20sales.%20But%20unions%20opposed%20the%20closures%20and%20GM%20only%20received%20judicial%20approval%20to%20exit%20India%20completely%20in%20January.%20The%20U.S.%20carmaker%20declined%20to%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20such%20difficulties%2C%20companies%20end%20up%20using%20contract%20workers%20for%20extended%20periods%2C%20said%20labour%20lawyer%20Amrish%20Patel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHSBC%20economists%20said%20that%20sweeping%20changes%20to%20labour%20regulations%20as%20well%20as%20land%20reforms%20are%20needed%20to%20sustain%20high%20growth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20to%20investors%20last%20month%2C%20HSBC%20economist%20Pranjul%20Bhandari%20wrote%20that%20such%20reforms%20could%20allow%20India%20to%20grow%20at%207.5-8%25%20over%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20creating%20a%20wealth%20of%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20lawyer%20and%20union%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singhvi%20said%20nearly%2060%25%20of%20the%20workers%20who%20benefit%20from%20current%20labour%20laws%20would%20lose%20protections%20if%20the%20BJP's%20codes%20are%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraveen%20Chakravarty%2C%20a%20senior%20economics%20policy%20official%20with%20the%20main%20opposition%20Congress%2C%20told%20Reuters%20that%20labour%20law%20decisions%20should%20be%20left%20to%20the%20states.%20His%20party's%20manifesto%20calls%20for%20a%20review%20of%20the%20labour%20codes%20passed%20by%20parliament.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETariff%20Land%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManufacturing%20costs%20in%20India%20are%20also%20elevated%20because%20of%20tariffs%20on%20imports%2C%20including%20components%20for%20high-end%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20encourage%20smartphone%20production%2C%20Delhi%20cut%20import%20duties%20on%20components%20to%2010%25.%20But%20competitor%20Vietnam%20already%20levies%20a%20rate%20of%20between%200%25%20and%205%25%20on%20equivalent%20inputs%2C%20according%20to%20the%20India%20Cellular%20and%20Electronics%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20import%20tariff%20imposed%20by%20India%20on%20World%20Trade%20Organisation%20(WTO)%20members%20was%2018.1%25%2C%20compared%20to%207.5%25%20for%20China%2C%20according%20to%20WTO%20data%20for%202022%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20year%20for%20which%20figures%20are%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustoms%20processes%20are%20also%20significantly%20quicker%20and%20less%20burdensome%20in%20China%2C%20said%20Gao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImports%20can%20clear%20customs%20in%20China%20in%20about%2020%20hours%2C%20said%20the%20SMU%20professor.%20It%20takes%20between%2044%20and%2085%20hours%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20a%202023%20government%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20focused%20its%20efforts%20on%20being%20a%20key%20node%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20rather%20than%20attempting%20to%20own%20the%20entire%20chain%2C%20leading%20to%20greater%20efficiencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20products%20exported%20by%20China%20often%20include%20inputs%20from%20other%20Northeast%20Asian%20countries%2C%20said%20Christian%20de%20Guzman%20of%20Moody's%20Ratings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Delhi%20%26quot%3Bwants%20to%20have%20the%20entire%20thing%20come%20onshore%2C%26quot%3B%20Guzman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717397760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F3ng1iro_pm-modi-pti_625x300_01_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fpm-modi-plans-post-election-reforms-to-rival-chinese-manufacturing-5803954%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20plans%20a%20raft%20of%20business-friendly%20measures%20if%20he%20wins%20a%20third%20term%20this%20week%2C%20including%20pushing%20through%20regulations%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20hire%20and%20fire%20workers%2C%20according%20to%20two%20government%20officials%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fpm-modi-plans-post-ele