s%20exit%20polls%20predict%20a%20landslide%20victory%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECitigroup%20Inc.%20and%20Jefferies%20Financial%20Services%20Inc.%20see%20manufacturing%20and%20electric%20vehicles%20among%20other%20the%20key%20winners%20if%20exit%20polls%20translate%20into%20a%20similar%20result%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20when%20votes%20are%20counted%20June%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20term%20for%20PM%20Modi%20is%20seen%20by%20some%20investors%20as%20bolstering%20economy%20and%20markets%20as%20the%20promise%20of%20policy%20continuity%20attracts%20global%20capital.%20While%20stock%20traders%20are%20positioning%20themselves%20for%20sectors%20that%20will%20likely%20benefit%20from%20the%20election%20outcome%2C%20bond%20markets%20will%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20government%20finances%20and%20the%20July%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStock%20benchmark%20NSE%20Nifty%2050%20Index%20jumped%20as%20much%20as%203.6%25%20on%20Monday%20to%20a%20new%20intraday%20record.%20Indexes%20for%20infrastructure%20and%20state-owned%20firms%20on%20the%20NSE%20also%20rose%20sharply%20to%20their%20all-time%20highs%20in%20early%20trading%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rupee%20and%20bonds%20gained.%20The%20currency%20strengthened%20by%20the%20most%20since%20March%202023%20to%2082.9725%20against%20the%20dollar%2C%20according%20to%20prices%20compiled%20by%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20market%20participants%20are%20saying%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurendra%20Goyal%2C%20a%20strategist%20at%20Citigroup%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20the%20government%20to%20retain%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20energy%20and%20electric%20vehicles%20through%20reforms%2C%20budgetary%20allocations%2C%20and%20policy%20incentives.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStocks%20positively%20exposed%20to%20the%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%20and%20manufacturing%20growth%20would%20gain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESantanu%20Sengupta%2C%20senior%20economist%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20balance%2C%20most%20clients%20we%20met%20with%20in%20recent%20months%20appeared%20to%20infer%20that%20political%20continuity%20would%20contribute%20to%20a%20stable%20macro-economic%20environment%20and%20continuing%20reforms.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20narrow%20current%20account%20deficit%2C%20and%20adequate%20FX%20reserves%20means%20that%20the%20rupee%20offers%20resilient%20carry%20in%20a%20'stronger%20for%20longer'%20dollar%20world%2C%20among%20most%20EMs.%20Additionally%2C%20inflation%20is%20back%20within%20the%20RBI's%20target%20range%2C%20and%20a%20consolidating%20fiscal%20deficit%20(from%20high%20levels)%20means%20that%20IGBs%2C%20that%20are%20soon%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20JPM%20EM%20bond%20index%2C%20remain%20an%20attractive%20source%20of%20low-vol%20yield%20for%20fixed-income%20investors.%20We%20continue%20to%20recommend%20long%202-year%20IGBs%20and%20short%20EUR%2FINR%2C%20and%20our%20equity%20strategists%20continue%20to%20see%20further%20upside%20in%20equities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahesh%20Nandurkar%2C%20strategist%20at%20Jefferies%20Financial%20Group%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20cyclical%20upturn%20is%20underway%20in%20private%20capex%2C%20and%20political%20stability%20alongside%2C%20continues%20to%20make%20us%20like%20capex%20plays%20(real%20estate%2C%20industrials%2C%20power)%20from%20a%20long-term%20perspective.%20However%2C%20a%20tactical%20breather%20is%20likely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishnu%20Varathan%2C%20chief%20economist%20Asia%20ex-Japan%20at%20Mizuho%20Bank%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElections%20admittedly%20stole%20the%20thunder%2C%20but%20the%20wider%20economy%20has%20bragging%20rights%20to%20a%20hat%20trick%20of%20its%20own%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20trio%20of%20stellar%20growth%20outrun%2C%20S%26amp%3BP's%20pos