2Fa%3E%20in%20rural%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20collaborate%20with%20various%20NGO%20partners%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20factories%20to%20offer%20subsidised%20schemes%2C%20making%20the%20Asan%20Cup%20more%20accessible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIra%20engages%20with%20women%20from%20SHG%2C%20trains%20them%20and%20then%20sends%20them%20to%20villages%20to%20introduce%20women%20with%20the%20Asan%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ira%20Guha%2C%20founder%20of%20Asan%20Cup.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351636%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIra%20Guha%2C%20founder%20of%20Asan%20Cup.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20recipient%20receives%20a%20clutch%20storage%20pouch%2C%20a%20user%20manual%20in%20their%20local%20language%2C%20and%20a%20detailed%20educational%20session%20conducted%20by%20a%20local%20health%20worker.%20They%20also%20receive%20the%20health%20worker%E2%80%99s%20contact%20for%20follow-up%20sessions%20over%20the%20next%20six%20months.%20This%20comprehensive%20programme%20ensures%20that%20everyone%20has%20the%20resources%20and%