modular%3B%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Esilbattas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20been%20replaced%20by%20grinders%20and%20mixers.%20Although%20electronic%20machines%20have%20made%20our%20lives%20easier%2C%20the%20taste%20achieved%20through%20grinding%20in%20%3Cem%3Esilbattas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecan%E2%80%99t%20be%20got%20through%20modern%20equipment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20a%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20salt%20is%20pounded%20without%20any%20heat.%20This%20keeps%20the%20natural%20taste%20and%20flavours%20intact.%20In%20a%20grinder%2C%20the%20food%20is%20just%20cut%20into%20very%20fine%20pieces%20and%20not%20pounded%20to%20be%20properly%20mixed.%20When%20you%20use%20a%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20actually%20blending%20all%20the%20oils%20of%20the%20herbs%20and%20spices%20together%20to%20enhance%20the%20flavours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%20was%20determined%20to%20revive%20the%20traditional%20practice%20of%20using%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20With%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%20160%2C%20he%20bought%20the%20grinding%20stone%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20fresh%20coriander%2C%20and%20green%20chillies%2C%20and%20kicked%20off%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pisyun%20loon%20is%20a%20pahadi%20salt%20which%20is%20prepared%20by%20hand%20grounding%20spices%20and%20herbs%20on%20silbatta%20(traditional%20grinding%20stone).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351422%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPisyun%20loon%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20%3Cem%3Epahadi%20%3C%2Fem%3Esalt%20prepared%20by%20hand%20grounding%20spices%20and%20herbs%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3E%20(traditional%20grinding%20stone).%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20market%20the%20products%2C%20Sandeep%20and%20his%20friends%20set%20up%20a%20stall%20at%20a%20local%20fair.%20%E2%80%9COur%20products%20were%20so%20loved%20that%20we%20were%20out%20of%20stock%20on%20the%20third%20day.%20We%20got%20a%20great%20response%20from%20both%20locals%20as%20well%20as%20tourists.%20Later%20in%20Haldwani%2C%20we%20set%20up%20a%20stall%20and%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%201.5%20to%202%20lakh%20in%20seven%20days.%20Our%20work%20was%20featured%20in%20local%20news%2C%20and%20with%20that%2C%20we%20earned%20fame%20and%20started%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20orders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back%20for%20Sandeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20HimFla%20manufactures%20up%20to%2020%20quintals%20of%20flavoured%20salt%20to%20cater%20to%20their%20customers%20in%20India%20and%20worldwide%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Australia%2C%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Dubai%2C%20Germany%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Brazil.%20Today%2C%20the%20startup%E2%80%99s%20annual%20revenue%20stands%20at%20Rs%201.5%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmploying%20rural%20households%20with%20dignity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20five%20flavours%20%E2%80%94%20garlic%20green%20chilli%2C%20garlic%20red%20chilli%2C%20garlic%20yellow%20chilli%2C