20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20sustainable%20and%20organic%20living%20was%20being%20circulated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20realised%20that%20it%20might%20be%20the%20right%20time%20to%20switch%20and%20give%20people%20an%20alternative%20to%20regular%20icecreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20not%20target%20the%20market%20for%20organic%20icecreams%3F%E2%80%99%20Considering%20the%20popularity%20of%20organic%20products%20like%20biscuits%2C%20%3Cem%3Enamkeen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20even%20%3Cem%3Eagarbatti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20opportunity.%20There%20are%20even%20brands%20for%20organic%20smokes%2C%20so%20why%20not%20icecream%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20the%20company%20started%20producing%20organic%20icecreams.%20%E2%80%9CRegarding%20the%20product%2C%20we%20majorly%20focus%20on%20the%20ingredients.%20We%20use%20only%20the%20desi%20cow%20milk%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20have%20set%20up%20my%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20a%20tier%202%20town%20like%20Nellore.%20In%20larger%20cities%2C%20this%20milk%20is%20sold%20at%20approximately%20Rs%20150%20per%20litre%2C%20but%20in%20tier%202%20cities%2C%20I%20can%20get%20it%20for%20Rs%2050%20to%2060%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20awareness%20and%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20strategy%20allows%20him%20to%20achieve%20sustainable%20business%20growth%20by%20utilising%20local%20materials%20and%20cutting%20cost%2C%20he%20informs.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20replace%20sugar%20with%20%3Cem%3Emishri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20natural%20sweetener%2C%20in%20our%20icecream.%20We%20use%20organic%20butter%20and%20vegetable-extracted%20colours.%20Importantly%2C%20we%20do%20not%20use%20any%20preservatives%20or%20stabilisers%20in%20our%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20a%20product%20called%20edible%20gum%2C%20also%20called%20%3